All essential geological phenomena and processes taking place inside the Earth and on the surface are discussed and introduced. Basic knowledge of the evolution of the Earth, origin of rocks, minerals and mineral resources is acquired. Introduction into Estonian geology and minreal resources.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Students will acquire knowledge on principal geodynamic processes and Earth evolution, to identify main rock types. Students will learn basic principles of Earth origin and evolution, and geological structure of Estonia.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Successful student: * knows main endogenic and exogenic geological processes taking place on the Earth * has knowledge on the Earths inner structure * has basic knowledge and is able to identify main rock types and minerals * knows geological evolution of the Earth * has acquired main features of Estonian geology
